TITLE: Setting Color Properties in React Native Skia
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates different ways to set colors in React Native Skia components using CSS color strings, hexadecimal numbers in ARGB format, and HSL notation.

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import {Group, Circle, vec} from "@shopify/react-native-skia";

<>
  <Group color="red">
    <Circle c={vec(0, 0)} r={100} />
  </Group>
  {/* 0xffff0000 is also red (format is argb) */}
  <Group color={0xffff0000}>
    <Circle c={vec(0, 0)} r={50} />
  </Group>
  {/* Any CSS color is valid */}
  <Group color="hsl(120, 100%, 50%)">
    <Circle c={vec(0, 0)} r={50} />
  </Group>
</>
```

