TITLE: Creating Paths Using SVG Notation in React Native Skia
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to create a path in React Native Skia using SVG path notation. The path defines a star shape using the SVG path format with move (M), line (L), and close (Z) commands.

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import {Canvas, Path} from "@shopify/react-native-skia";

const SVGNotation = () => {
  return (
    <Canvas style={{ flex: 1 }}>
      <Path
        path="M 128 0 L 168 80 L 256 93 L 192 155 L 207 244 L 128 202 L 49 244 L 64 155 L 0 93 L 88 80 L 128 0 Z"
        color="lightblue"
      />
    </Canvas>
  );
};
