TITLE: Low-level Font API Usage in React Native Skia
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating the low-level font APIs that power the matchFont function. This shows how to access the system font manager, create custom font managers, and match fonts with specific styles.

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import {Platform} from "react-native";
import {Skia, FontStyle} from "@shopify/react-native-skia";

