TITLE: Creating Animated Rectangle Buffers with useRectBuffer in React Native Skia
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create and animate an array of rectangles using the useRectBuffer hook. This buffer can be used with components that accept rectangle arrays like the Atlas API.

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import {useRectBuffer} from "@shopify/react-native-skia";

const width = 256;
const size = 10;
const rects = 100;
// Important to not forget the worklet directive
const rectBuffer = useRectBuffer(rects, (rect, i) => {
  "worklet";
  rect.setXYWH((i * size) % width, Math.floor(i / (width / size)) * size, size, size);
});
```

